form.blog-info-12(data-request-validate data-element="blog-phone")
  .blog-info-12__title(data-element="form-enter-sms-title") Узнайте реальный уровень знаний ребёнка
  picture.blog-info-12__picture
    source(srcset=staticImg('blog-info-12/decor-1_xxs.svg') media="(max-width: 359px)")
    source(srcset=staticImg('blog-info-12/decor-1_mob.svg') media="(max-width: 743px)")
